Follow the doc mentioned at https://ajorloo.medium.com/deploy-rocket-chat-server-using-kubernetes-2d6c4228853

After applying the yaml run the following commands in the mongo DB

```cmd

$ kubectl exec -it rocketmongo-0 mongo

rs.initiate()
var config = rs.conf()
config.members[0].host="rocketmongo-0.rocketmongo:27017"
rs.reconfig(config)
rs.add("rocketmongo-1.rocketmongo:27017")
rs.add("rocketmongo-2.rocketmongo:27017")
rs.status()

```

Then you can configure it on <IP>/setup-wizard